              <h2>How to use this RSVP tracker</h2>
              <p>
                This tool is designed to replace messy spreadsheets and paper
                lists. It works entirely in your browser: nothing is uploaded to
                a server. You can export your data at any time as CSV or JSON
                for backup or sharing.
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>
                  <strong>Set your event details</strong> – Enter the event
                  name, date, and RSVP deadline at the top.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Add your guest list</strong> – For each invitation,
                  add:
                  <ul>
                    <li>Guest name (or couple/family name)</li>
                    <li>
